properties.areaDesc: Waters from Lower Atchafalaya River to Intracoastal City LA from 20 to 60 NM; Waters from Intracoastal City to Cameron LA from 20 to 60 NM; Waters from Cameron LA to High Island TX from 20 to 60 NM
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 16 at 9:25AM CST until January 16 at 9:00PM CST by NWS Lake Charles LA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to one quarter mile or
less.

* WHERE...Waters from Cameron LA to High Island TX from 20 to 60
NM, Waters from Intracoastal City to Cameron LA from 20 to 60
NM and Waters from Lower Atchafalaya River to Intracoastal
City LA from 20 to 60 NM.

* WHEN...Until 9 PM CST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 PM CST THIS EVENING
